         <children>
            <Text fill="WHITE" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="You now understand the different permissions on a file, now it's time to change them.&#10;&#10;There are a couple of ways to change permissions, but first we'll start by adding execute permissions on a file." wrappingWidth="470.0" VBox.vgrow="ALWAYS">
               <font>
