            <Text fill="WHITE" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="You can also change permissions another way, using a numerical format, instead of using r, w, or x you can use numbers.&#10;&#10;The numerical representations are:&#10;&#10;4: read permission&#10;2: write permission&#10;1: execute permission&#10;&#10;So here is an example:" wrappingWidth="456.0">
